folder: Willowbrook Road & Sunset Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
Willowbrook Road, north side, at Sunset Avenue (formerly Gun Factory Road), showing an old dwelling having belonged to Schmul in 1853. In 1874 it was owned by Gotman; in 1907 by
H. Vallencia; and in 1917 by Henrico Vincent.
May 9, 1926
P. L. Sperr

folder: Willowbrook Road & Sunset Avenue, Staten Island, NY
text:
Willowbrook Road, south side, about 200 feet west of Sunset Avenue (formerly Gun Factory Road), showing the remains of an old stone-and-wood dwelling. In 1853 it was the property of E. Houghwout; in 1874 of Allgire; and from 1898 to 1917 of
Adam Allgnar.
July 18, 1926
P. L. Sperr
